# Substrate is per-project — never gitignored at framework level.
# Individual amanuensis workspaces decide whether to git-track their substrate
# (typically yes — that's the audit trail).
#
# Replay log IS substrate (audit trail) and IS committed; do NOT add
# replay-log/ to .gitignore.

# Plans live OUTSIDE the project at ~/Documents/Projects/.plans/{project}/
# (deliberately, for cross-project metrics). Not relevant to .gitignore.

# Imported-research artifacts — kept locally for the maintainer's
# reference but NOT published. The architecture rationale they captured
# has already been distilled into `docs/architecture.md` and
# `INVARIANTS.md`. To republish a sanitised excerpt, hand-edit and
# commit specific files from a clean branch — do not bulk-add either
# directory.
research-transcripts/
synthesis/
MANIFEST.md

# Original research zip — large; replace with synthesis/ extract
brainstorming-distillation-*.zip
